description: The word "back" with an arrow above it, pointing to the left.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the back arrow emoji is a sleek, dynamic symbol featuring a clean, white arrowhead pointing left, set against a vibrant, circular blue background. The glossy sheen and subtle 3D effect give it a polished, modern feel, characteristic of Apple's user interface design. This emoji is essential for navigation, indicating a return to a previous screen or action within apps on Apple devices.
